msgid ""
"Output the create options XML column of JPEG as a table. These creator "
"options can be used in the ST_AsGDALRaster options argument."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This example turns a few common GeoTIFF creator options into a compact table."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <function>XMLTABLE</function> to expose selected GTiff creation options "
"as rows. The same pattern can be used without the name filter to inspect the "
"full XML document."
msgstr ""

